        {
            "title": "新盤成交插九成｜雅盈峰連沽8伙吸2億｜200客爭SIERRA SEA 2B期1撻訂戶 提價後最終551萬成交",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蛇年最後一個周末，未有大型新盤推售，樓市交投轉趨淡靜。周末兩日（14至15日）一手市場僅錄得約34宗成交，較對上一周約287宗大跌近九成。市場焦點主要落於中環豪宅雅盈峰。反觀二手市場持續疲弱，四大代理十大屋苑成交量全線報跌，全屬單位數，介乎4至8宗，跌幅由約一成至五成不等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>雅盈峰兩日沽8伙  大手客掃全層</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由盈大地產及資本策略合作發展的中環雅盈峰，周末兩日（14及15日）共沽8伙，套現近2億元。其中一組大手投資客斥資逾1億元，掃入8樓全層6伙，呎價由33,600至35,399元不等。。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-372cef7a-add9-3c61-8cee-fe52e396fb3b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該盤另外兩宗成交，分別為16樓C室及17樓B室，實用面積1,017及1,074平方呎，同屬三房戶，成交價分別為4,261.23萬及5,133.72萬元，呎價約47,800及41,900元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">承接熱賣氣勢，發展商隨即加推2伙三房戶，並上載銷售安排，定於大年初一（17日）及初四（20日）招標。項目累售22伙，套現逾9.1億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇雅盈峰價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/408ON4G\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇雅盈峰價單】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wg.CBH44QwTDugrN6p5E5g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/8cd43f2540f197315bccdd41f517978d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖一：雅盈峰</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>維港‧灣畔1B期沽3伙 吸金約5200萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國海外等發展的啟德臨海盤維港‧灣畔1B期，周末（14及15日）售出3伙，吸金約5,196.2萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">成交單位包括第2B座23樓C室，實用面積569平方呎，屬三房間隔，成交價1,867.5萬元，呎價32,821元。另外兩伙均為第2B座J室兩房連儲物房單位，實用面積同為549平方呎，其中11樓J室以1,635.1萬元售出，呎價29,783元；而19樓J室成交價則為1,693.6萬元，呎價30,848元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該盤開售至今累沽205伙，總成交額逾36億元，平均每伙成交價逾1,750萬元，平均呎價約3萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇維港‧灣畔1B期價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/48TwDcl\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇維港‧灣畔1B期價單】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d1rXEkShZzUTSExq_wgKBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/c33a7f2c79b148a42ed1df4ad37b3f7c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖二：維港‧灣畔1B期</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>海德園單日套現逾2,812萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">太古地產與中華汽車合作發展的柴灣海德園，周日(15日)錄得3宗成交，單日吸金逾2,812萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3伙均為3座G室，分布於9樓、10樓及12樓，實用面積554平方呎，屬兩房連梗廚間隔，成交價介乎923.7萬至948.9萬元，呎價約16,673至17,128元；當中最高成交價為12樓G室，作價948.9萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">項目自去年9月開售以來，累錄128宗成交，套現逾11億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">示範單位設於太古坊康橋大廈8樓及9樓，農曆新年期間（年廿九至初三）照常開放，時間為中午12時至晚上7時。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇海德園價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4inL9fM\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇海德園價單】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nt7J5mkze32gWUte_wzk7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/a7e2349eea0cd0a56ba72a97a17fa533\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖三：海德園</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>SIERRA SEA 2B期1撻訂戶加價重推 200客爭崩頭搶高至551萬</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得留意的是，新地西沙SIERRA SEA系列屬蛇年熱銷盤，去年4月至今累售逾3,000伙。第2B期一伙早前撻訂單位，於周六（14日）早上抽籤重售，吸引逾200組向隅客爭購，場面墟冚。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該單位為3座12樓J室，實用面積433平方呎，月初原以525萬元售出，當時呎價12,125元。發展商收回單位後加價約5%，將折實價調升至532.44萬元，對應折實呎價12,297元。最終單位以551.23萬元成交，呎價達12,730元，足見需求殷切。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇SIERRA SEA 2B期價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4jTYKvT\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇SIERRA SEA 2B期價單】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7ueeJagIvQOSn6jevGke9w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/a072e29364cee503a71c609b4f29cbed\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖四：SIERRA SEA 2B期</strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x18L3b.qpo_rhZbSNJVCCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/efb63784c62e673cde6ddd22ae491c70\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖五：周末(2月14日-2月15日)一手新盤成交統計</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>二手全線下滑 買家準備收爐</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">反觀二手市場持續疲弱，價量齊跌。隨著農曆新年臨近，買家陸續「收爐」，四大代理十大屋苑周末成交量全線報跌。其中中原地產錄得5宗成交，較上周的8宗大幅回落，按周急跌37.5%，連跌兩周並創26周新低，當中半數屋苑「零成交」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個別屋苑錄得蝕讓個案，元朗RESIDENCE譽88一伙兩房戶持貨約7年貶值近百萬元。成交單位為1座高層A室，實用面積505平方呎，原開價610萬元，最終減價14萬元，以596萬元沽出，呎價11,802元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據悉，新買家為上車客，鍾情屋苑交通方便，加上單位內櫳企理、價錢合理，遂迅速購入自用。原業主早於2019年7月以695萬元入市，持貨約7年，帳面虧損99萬元，期內樓價貶值約14%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇RESIDENCE譽88放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tLx8Of\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇RESIDENCE譽88放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:雅盈峰;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/雅盈峰\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">雅盈峰</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Sierra Sea 2B期;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/sierra-sea-2b-期\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Sierra Sea 2B期</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Sierra Sea;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/Sierra-Sea-33180\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Sierra Sea</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:康橋大廈;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/康橋大廈-27124\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">康橋大廈</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:海德園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/海德園-32959\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">海德園</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:太古坊;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/office/detail/太古坊-32117\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">太古坊</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:中環;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/中環-27339\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中環</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:柴灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/柴灣-27355\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">柴灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:啟德;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/啟德-27394\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">啟德</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:元朗;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/元朗-27400\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">元朗</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%8F%92%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90-%E9%9B%85%E7%9B%88%E5%B3%B0%E9%80%A3%E6%B2%BD8%E4%BC%99%E5%90%B82%E5%84%84-200%E5%AE%A2%E7%88%ADSIERRA-SEA-2B%E6%9C%9F1%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82%E6%88%B6-%E6%8F%90%E5%83%B9%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82551%E8%90%AC%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4-74626\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
