        {
            "title": "二手蝕讓｜牛潭尾意花園洋房1480萬沽 9年蝕789.9萬 貶值35％",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"520\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/o3EGSHZ0nlWqO69hkFWTCA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/79f2e4ab8ad20d3a308052f7e441bf09\" width=\"653\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本港樓市反彈，但就不是處處彈得起。9年前的雞年首個新盤長實（1113）牛潭尾意花園最新錄得一宗二手成交，一個1,638方呎的洋房單位以1,480萬元成交，原業主帳面勁蝕789.8萬元，單位貶值35％。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美聯物業譚秀琼表示，上述意花園單位為米萊諾大道單號屋，實用面積1,638方呎，4房4套間隔，另連花園約834方呎及435方呎天台，地下設車位，1樓及2樓為睡房區，在農曆新年前以1,480萬元成交，呎價9,035元。買家為長線投資客，見樓價吸引，決定加快拍板入市。資料顯示，原業主於2017年以約2,269.8萬元購入上述物業，持貨約9年，是次轉手帳面蝕讓約789.8萬元，物業期內貶值約35%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c7b263d9-32a0-302f-b24b-7d371fb8a11d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長實牛潭尾意花園為2017年雞年首個開價新盤，當年現樓賣，首批30伙折實平均呎價約15,069元，較2016年同系新盤洋房元朗屏山娉廷高約25%，並較同區二手高約兩成。來到今日，樓盤二手成交疏落，蝕多過賺，去年一個雙號屋，實用面積一樣1,638方呎，以1,499萬元成交，原業主持貨8年，帳面蝕944萬元，單位貶值39％。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:免費地產投資講座\nhttps://rb.gy/nl0vm9;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://rb.gy/nl0vm9\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">免費地產投資講座<br/>https://rb.gy/nl0vm9</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Be your own boss, keep your mind sharp.<br/>🌟更多資訊，盡在<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:BossMind;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bossmindmedia\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">BossMind</a><br/>https://www.facebook.com/bossmindmedia</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93-%E7%89%9B%E6%BD%AD%E5%B0%BE%E6%84%8F%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E6%B4%8B%E6%88%BF1480%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD-9%E5%B9%B4%E8%9D%95789-9%E8%90%AC-%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC35-034208186.html",
